CardStreams,REST,API,has,stream,based,storage,and,retrieval,architecture,This,API,allows,for,the,creation,storage,curation,and,distribution,of,content,to,display,in,activity,streams,feeds,CardStreams,REST,API,uses,GET,posts,and,provides,REST,responses,and,requires,a,authentication,token,There,are,three,levels,of,API,access,plans,ranging,from,free,for,developers,with,a,call,daily,and,streams,limit,to,an,Enterprise,level,with,unlimited,developer,accounts,CardStreams,is,a,cloud,based,platform,for,SaaS,streams,that,provides,micro,content,for,mobile,web,and,desktop,applications